Steps: 1000
Final energy: -12.45

EQUILIBRIUM CONCEPT POSITIONS:
  skill     [0.42, 0.73] trit=+1 (hub)
  MCP       [0.38, 0.71] trit=0  (near skill)
  thermal   [0.15, 0.22] trit=-1 (isolated)

THERMAL CLUSTERS:
  Cluster 1 (T=0.01): [skill, MCP, subagent] E=-8.2
